### 注册新用户 Chloe
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "chloe",
  "email": "chloe@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "securityQuestion": "Who's your best friend?",
  "securityAnswer": "Alice",
  "notes": "Chloe for registration test"
}

### 登录 Chloe
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 请求重置密码（获取 security question）
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/reset-question
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "chloe@example.com"
}

### 验证安全问题答案（获得 reset token）
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/verify-answer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "chloe@example.com",
  "securityAnswer": "Alice"
}

### 重置密码
PATCH http://localhost:8000/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

